{"title":"“沙里淘金”者","authors":["邹荻帆"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“沙里淘金”者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邹荻帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大会展开斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反击右派言行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这位同志的态度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“冷静”有如寒冰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“难道他全盘讲错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总该沙里淘金！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他说百花齐放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要党的领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当然这是错误。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他也要党放心、容忍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主张鸣而不争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他骂人事单位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等于公安部门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然语言诬蔑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足证意见在心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文人夸夸其谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍蝇大象不分。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“沙里淘金”，多好听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似蓝天碧波海鸥鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派要凿穿海船底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船沉海底谁淘金？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥上下为谁唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥、海鸥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本来没有爱社会主义的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你呢，“沙里淘金”的人？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}